    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a meticulously maintained 2004 BMW M3, a pinnacle of the E46 chassis. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system recently overhauled to ensure surgical throttle response. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels through a variable M differential lock. This specimen has received a documented subframe reinforcement, mitigating the platform's primary structural concern. The suspension geometry is preserved with refreshed bushings and dampers, providing the signature communicative feedback expected of an M-division icon. With factory-spec paint depth and a pristine underside, this vehicle satisfies the most rigorous mechanical and aesthetic standards.",
