      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen that looks and smells exactly as it did on the showroom floor. Finished in a flawless deep metallic paint with a multi-stage ceramic coating, the exterior is devoid of even the slightest swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Inside, the premium leather seats remain supple and firm, showing absolutely no bolster wear or discoloration. Every electronic component, from the heads-up display to the climate-controlled seating, operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach; it has been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a complete, paper-trail documented history included in the sale. Garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in rain or snow, the undercarriage is as pristine as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity to own a single-owner, non-smoker vehicle that has been meticulously maintained to the highest possible standard. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
